{"id":217450,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":3,"day":5}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"182","ytitle":"","mtitle":"粉碎美帝侵略的梦想!","ftitle":"","authors":["方向"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"方向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反对片面媾和，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反对重新武装日本!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是天经地义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正义的呼声!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年血债未清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万人深仇埋在心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒的火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧五万万人的胸膛!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝又放出战犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张牙舞爪!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦想——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再把中国当屠场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血腥地奸淫烧杀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦想!——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把东方升起的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推到海底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再把世界变成黑暗!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来!起来!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲的人民!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出铁掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠狠地一拳!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打破美帝猪鼻子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎它侵略的梦想!"}]}